{"tid":456511,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"高先生獨白嘆終睇透炒家心態","createTime":"2017-11-03T04:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T14:13:32.000Z","uid":34444,"like":262,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"16a156609d010457157652297bebf4932daf8eac","tid":456511,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/122718_16f6d757cf3b562e6aa480bb6882792b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F122718_16f6d757cf3b562e6aa480bb6882792b.jpg&h=e04418cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高先生成功預約2部太空灰iPhone X 256GB，今晨9時半與太太到銅鑼灣取機。他稱自己都有意換手機，但希望在首輪先賺一轉，現在候價待沽。但他取機後聽聞收機價約只有1.1萬元，他稱若價錢再無上升都會選擇放機。他承認，早前曾希望收機價可達3萬元，「但現實和幻想始終差好遠。」<span style=\"color: red;\">他認為是炒家唱高價錢以吸引果農入貨，令現在貨量充足就壓低收購價。</span><br />\n<br />\n依加先知，豬到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7910c837694c3527bcdee5ea1a8ad7defc31e68f","tid":456511,"uid":34444,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/123354_71f9bcaa60a596dce96bb132f2ba1dbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F123354_71f9bcaa60a596dce96bb132f2ba1dbd.jpg&h=be90c992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLo哥收咗皮未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba221b62487df3328b193a27bb9ffb5317ff2b7c","tid":456511,"uid":511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"炒炒炒，炒你老味咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid